BP classification. BU-owned = Parent BP belongs to a specific BU; CPs under it inherit Owning BU from this row's Target BU. Horizontal = Parent BP is centrally owned (no specific BU); CPs under it have no Owning BU and anchor to the BP itself for applicability (per ADR-040). Unresolved = default for newly imported BPs awaiting admin classification at Stage 3. Manual override field pattern not applicable here — classification IS the manual signal.
